  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a GNOME Online Accounts</title>

    <para>
      The <application>GNOME Online Accounts</application> package contains a
framework used to access the user's online accounts.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Informação do Pacote</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Transferência (HTTP): <ulink url="&gnome-online-accounts-download-http;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
